  "doc_id": "36023",
  "text": "Patient and public involvement has become an integral part of health services [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . It has progressed from simple patient satisfaction surveys to public forums debating service developments and budget. Role players take part in undergraduate and postgraduate medical examinations [CITATION_5] , patient feedback is included in periodic appraisals of medical practitioners and regulatory bodies include lay members on their panels. Patient representatives comment on medical guidelines and research proposals [CITATION_6] .",
